title: SUCI 4 - Stand Up Comedy Dodit: PECAH! Saya Jawa, tapi Megang Erat Budaya Eropa
tags: DODIT KOMIKA|KOMIKA DODIT|DODIT|STAND UP COMEDY INDONESIA|SUCI 4
description: Dodit Wahyudi Mulyanto atau lebih dikenal dengan Dodit merupakan kontestan dari Stand Up Comedy Indonesia (SUCI) 4. Ciri khas yang paling mudah diingat dalam penampilan Dodit saat di panggung adalah pembawaannya yang kalem dan membawa biola, meski kadang tidak dimainkan.---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------SUCI 9 akan kembali lagi untuk menemani para pecinta setia Stand Up Comedy Indonesia, setelah vakum selama 1 tahun.Sambil menunggu hadirnya SUCI 9 di layar kaca, tim KompasTV akan menampilkan kembali video-video yang menarik sekaligus mengundang tawa para penonton Stand Up Comedy.SUCI akan bernostalgia melalui tayangan video dari SUCI 1 sampai SUCI 8.Tentunya dengan penampilan dari komika-komika ternama, yang pada waktu itu sedang merintis karier mereka.Untuk para pecinta SUCI yang mau request upload, silakan tinggalkan komen di bawah ya.Follow Stand Up Comedy KompasTV di Instagram: @sucikompastv untuk tahu informasi-informasi terupdate Stand Up Comedy Kompas TV, termasuk jadwal audisi.#DoditMulyanto #SUCI4 #Dodit

description: Baru-baru ini beredar kabar bahwa Kim Jong Un, pemimpin Korea Utara sakit parah dan kondisinya kritis pasca melakukan prosedur kardiovaskular (jantung). Semenjak saat itu, informasi yang simpang siur memicu spekulasi mengenai kesehatan Kim Jong Un. Namun terdapat informasi menarik di balik hal tersebut, di mana media berhasil menghimpun siapa yang kira-kira akan mengambil alih kursi pemimpin negara jika Kim Jong Un sakit parah atau bahkan meninggal dunia. Dari seluruh calon, terdapat 2 kandidat wanita yang diperkirakan bisa saja memimpin Korea Utara. description: Klik untuk berdonasi Kita Bisa Melawan Duniahttps://kitabisa.com/campaign/kitabisamelawanduniaRizky Febian Mengajak Anak Muda Untuk Melawan Demi DuniaDengan kondisi saat ini di seluruh dunia khususnya Indonesia, Rizky Febian tergerak hatinya untuk menulis lagu dengan harapan anak muda bisa terus semangat menjalani hidup untuk mencapai mimpinya. Lagu ini menjadi lagu penyemangat untuk kita semua yang harus percaya bahwa badai yang sedang terjadi akan segera berlalu. Dalam melewati masa pandemi ini, Rizky Febian juga berharap kita harus saling mendukung antar sesama. Kita semua punya peran untuk memberikan dukungan kepada tim medis yang menjadi garda terdepan penanganan virus corona ini dan mendukung para pekerja kreatif harian.Setelah Rizky Febian bekerja sama dengan Kitabisa.com sebelumnya dalam penggalangan dana yang disalurkan kepada pengemudi ojol (ojek-online), pedagang keliling dan pegawai medis. Kali ini, Rizky Febian berkampanye diiringi dengan lagu terbarunya berjudul “Melawan Demi Dunia”. Iky mengajak teman-teman untuk berdonasi yang hasilnya akan didistribusikan kepada para pekerja kreatif harian (crew) yang terkena dampak serius akibat pandemi ini. Donasi ini nanti akan berupa uang tunai yang akan dijadikan modal untuk memulai usaha baru berskala kecil, yang bisa dilakukan sementara selama Pandemi ini berlangsung.Sebagai rangkaian penggalangan donasi, Rizky Febian akan mengajak sesama musisi untuk Live Streaming bersama melalui akun Instagramnya. description: AMAZING ART TUTORIALS AND IDEAS YOU SHOULD TRYAre you looking to unleash your creative side? Well, in this video I show you some amazing tricks and hacks to help you become a better artist. Not only will these tips improve your art skills, but they’ll also help you experiment and find out which style suits you. For starters, you can add some glue on an eggshell and sprinkle some quarks to it. Then, add warm water in a glass bowl, add some food coloring, and some more quarks in the bowl and you’re all set.Another experiment you can try is the cotton candy vs water. You can add the cotton candy in water and then let it become liquid. I show you how to use glitter in your paints and some epoxy resin to create beautiful decorations for your home. One is to pour some glitter in some epoxy resin, mix it up and then pour the paint on round canvas to give some color to your room. I also show you how to use Coptic markers and to dry out some doodles for your bullet journal. Timestamps: 0:31 – How to grow crystals on an eggshell3:19 – Satisfying paint hacks4:51 – Amazing tricks using markers6:22 – Color changing doodles you should try8:34 – Glitter ideas you should try9:53 – Paint splatter painting This video is made for entertainment purposes. description: [더 킹 : 영원의 군주 OST Part 2] 화사 (Hwa Sa) - Orbit MV 입니다.화사 (Hwa Sa) - Orbit‘더 킹 : 영원의 군주’ 두 번째 OST '화사 - Orbit' 공개2020년 상반기 최고 기대작 SBS 새 금토드라마 ‘더 킹 : 영원의 군주’의 OST의 두 번째 가창자로 화사가 참여한다.지난 1, 2화 '더 킹'의 강렬한 엔딩 장면을 장식한 화사의 ‘Orbit’은 ‘더 킹’만의 환상적이고 세련된 분위기와 함께차원을 넘나드는 신비함 등을 표현하고 있으며, 사랑하는 이를 지켜주겠다는 다짐을 담고 있는 곡이다.또한 몽환적이면서도 강렬한 기타 사운드, 힙합 리듬이 더해진 트랙 위로화사의 강렬하고 파워풀한 보컬이 조화를 이룬다는 점에서 폭발적인 호응을 얻었다.특히, 화사가 데뷔 후 약 6년 만에 처음으로 OST 가창에 참여해 시청자들과 팬들의 기대를 모으는 한편,드라마 ‘더 킹’의 광활한 스케일과 역대급 판타지 로맨스 전개에 어울리는 'Orbit'을 통해 시청자들과 팬들에게 강렬한 인상을 남긴다.SBS ‘더 킹 : 영원의 군주’는 차원의 문(門)을 닫으려는 이과(理科) 형 대한제국 황제 이곤과누군가의 삶, 사람, 사랑을 지키려는 문과(文科) 형 대한민국 형사 정태을이두 세계를 넘나들며 펼치는 공조를 담아내는 드라마로, 매주 금, 토요일 오후 10시 방송된다.[Credit]Lyrics by 박우상, 소라Composed by 박우상Arranged by 박우상Guitar by 영Synthesizer by 박우상Chorus by 화사Mixed 조씨아저씨 @ Cube StudioMastered by 권남우 @821 Sound Mastering

title: Fold Up! It's Dumpling Time! 10 Doughy Dumpling Designs to Try at Home! So Yummy

description: Check out these 10 doughy dumpling designs to try at home! Let us know what your favorite dumpling design is in the comments below! For more doughy inspiration, cake decoration, and innovative recipes subscribe to So Yummy! Check out our cookbooks for fun and easy dessert ideas http://bit.ly/2WB2wzSSubscribe to So Yummy: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCH8NnRkxQg1zX7mHFRPq73g?sub_confirmation=1About So Yummy:So Yummy brings you fun food ideas and recipes for your cooking and baking adventures. We believe that home cooking should always be fun, interesting, and easy to do! Enjoy our collection of fun and easy food tutorials! With recipes ranging from healthy dinners to sugary sweet delights, there are a plethora of creative options to spice up your home cooking. Follow us:Facebook: http://bit.ly/SoYummyFBInstagram: http://bit.ly/SoYummyIGWebsite: https://soyummy.com/#SoYummy  #Dumpling #StayHomeDumpling DoughPrep Time1 hourDifficultyEasy Total Time1 hour Yield30-35 dumpling wrappersIngredients2 ¼ cups flour¾ cup warm water (between 110-120°F)Pinch of salt (optional)Instructions1. In a medium bowl, combine the flour and warm water until it becomes shaggy. With your hands, knead the shaggy dough inside the bowl until it comes together to form a ball. Cover the bowl with a damp towel and let rest for 15 minutes.2. After resting, transfer the ball of dough onto a clean surface and knead firmly until it becomes smooth and elastic (about 2-4 minutes.) Cover with a damp cloth and rest again, for 30 minutes.3. After the second rest, take your thumb and press firmly into the center of the dough ball. Using both hands, begin to squeeze and stretch the dough until you create a big donut shape with a large hole in the center. 4. Slice the “donut” into even pieces of desired size. Keep covered with a damp cloth, and when ready to use, roll pieces out individually into thin wrappers. (Optional: Trim wrappers using a large circle cookie cutter, for a clean edge.)5. Fill the wrappers with desired filling, and fold to form designs of your liking! Cook, eat, and enjoy.https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCH8NnRkxQg1zX7mHFRPq73g

tags: Syekh Ali Jaber|Ramadan|covid-19|medcom id
description: Pendakwah sekaligus Ulama Syekh Ali Jaber mengatakan, bulan suci Ramadan kali ini menjadi istimewa meskipun di tengah pandemi covid-19. Dirinya mengatakan aktivitas di bulan Ramadan dapat dilakukan dengan lebih khusyuk di rumah. Sambil terisak, dia juga mengungkapkan curahan hatinya terhadap orang yang masih keras kepala, tidak menaati aturan pemerintah untuk mencegah penyebaran virus korona. Sambil menyeka air mata, Ali meminta umat Islam tetap patuh beribadah dari rumah. Dia percaya Corona bisa dihadapi asal masyarakat mau berikhtiar.
